<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>POG CRATES</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../static/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div id="gamblingBanner">
        <h1 style="text-align: center;">POG CRATES</h1>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: center;">  
        <div id="buttonList">
            <h3>CRATES</h3>
            <button id="crate1">Common Crate - $100</button>
            <button id="crate2">Rare Crate - $500</button>
            <button id="crate3">Epic Crate - $1,000</button>
            <button id="crate4">Legendary Crate - $5,000</button>
            <button id="crate6">Mythical Crate- $10,000</button>
            <button id="crate5">Godly Crate - $100,000</button>
            <h3>UTILITIES</h3>
            <button id="upgradeinventory">Upgrade Inventory ($ per slot)</button>
        </div>
        <div id="money">Money: $1000</div>
        <h3 id="income"></h3>
        <h4 id="invTxt"></h4>
        <progress id="invPB" value="0" max="100"></progress>
        <div id="inventory"></div>
        </div>
        <div id="settings">
            <h3>SETTINGS</h3>
            <button id="save">Save</button>
            <button id="load">Load</button>
            <button id="reset">Reset</button>
            <h4 id="modeTxt">Light Mode</h4>
            <label class="switch">
                <input type="checkbox" id="darkmode">
                <span class="slider round"></span>
            </label>
            <br>
            <h4 id="sortTxt">Sort</h4>
            <div id="sortOptions" style="justify-content: center;">
                <button class="sort" id="bottomSort">Least Rare &darr;</button>
                <button class="sort" id="topSort">Most Rare &uarr;</button>
            </div>
            <h4>Patch Notes (Weekly)</h4>
            <p>Patch 0.0.1 - Week 5: 
                <ul style="text-align: left; margin-left: 5px; margin-right: 5px">
                    <li>-Added stack bonuses; 3+ of one rarity increases income of that rarity by 1.5x [indicated by a white glow outline]; 
                        all items will round to the nearest whole number</li>
                    <li>-Added sorting system from least to most rare</li>
                    <li>-Added cards for each rarity, including income and sell value</li>
                    <li>-Added scrollbar for the inventory rather than the website page</li>
                    <li>-Removed JSONS of rarities and crates to eliminate unnecessary redundancy</li>
                    <li>-Removed the dropdown for deleting items in the inventory; now each card has its own sell button</li>
                    <li>-Removed page scrolling; all data is stored on the single screen</li>
                    <li>-Added a failsafe that if all items are sold, then money will equal 200</li>
                    <li>-Edited the names of the crates to match their higher rarity chances</li>
                    <li>-Added Github functionality for collaboration</li>
                </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
<script src="../static/js/rarities.js"></script>
<script src="../static/js/crates.js"></script>
<script src="../static/js/stuffWork.js"></script>
</html>